Package: EconomicIndicatorsDashboard
Title: Global Economic Indicators Shiny Dashboard
Version: 1.0.0
Description: Interactive Shiny dashboard visualising GDP growth, inflation,
    and unemployment across 50+ countries using World Bank Open Data.
    Built with R, Shiny, dplyr, ggplot2, and Plotly.
Imports:
    shiny,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    plotly,
    wbstats,
    tidyr,
    DT
